@startuml
autonumber

box "Orchestration Layer" #LightCyan
participant "Camunda Engine" as Camunda
participant "Kong Gateway" as Kong
end box

box "Microservice Layer" #LightYellow
participant "Prosumer MS" as ProsumerMS
participant "Utility Operator MS" as UtilityMS
participant "Telemetry MS" as TelemetryMS
participant "Energy Analytics MS" as AnalyticsMS
end box

box "Messaging Layer" #Thistle
queue "Kafka Topic:\nEnergy-Discharged-By-Zone\n(Partition: ZoneID)" as KafkaZone
queue "Kafka Topic:\nGenerated-Energy-By-Prosumer\n(Partition: ProsumerID)" as KafkaGenPros
queue "Kafka Topic:\nConsumed-Energy-By-Prosumer\n(Partition: ProsumerID)" as KafkaConsPros
queue "Kafka Topic:\nAverage-SoC\n(Partition: ZoneID)" as KafkaSoC
end box

box "Persistence Layer" #LightGreen
database "AWS RDS" as DB
end box

== Data Gathering Phase (Orchestrated by Camunda) ==

Camunda -> Kong: GET /Prosumers \n(Fetch Prosumers & Assets)
Kong -> ProsumerMS: Forward Request
ProsumerMS -> DB: JDBC SELECT Prosumers and Assets
DB --> ProsumerMS: Result Set
ProsumerMS --> Kong: 200 OK\n{Prosumers[], Assets[]}
Kong --> Camunda: Prosumer Data Context

Camunda -> Kong: GET /UtilityOperators/GridCells \n(Fetch Zones)
Kong -> UtilityMS: Forward Request
UtilityMS -> DB: JDBC SELECT GridCells
DB --> UtilityMS: Result Set
UtilityMS --> Kong: 200 OK {GridCells[]}
Kong --> Camunda: Grid Zone Context

Camunda -> Kong: GET /Telemetry \n(Fetch recent metrics)
Kong -> TelemetryMS: Forward Request
TelemetryMS -> DB: JDBC SELECT Telemetry Records
DB --> TelemetryMS: Result Set
TelemetryMS --> Kong: 200 OK {TelemetryRecords[]}
Kong --> Camunda: Telemetry Context

== Energy Analytics Phase ==

Camunda -> Kong: POST /EnergyAnalytics/calculate\nPayload: {Prosumers, \nGridCells, Telemetry}
Kong -> AnalyticsMS: Forward Request

AnalyticsMS -> AnalyticsMS: Calculate "Energy Discharged by Zone"
AnalyticsMS -> AnalyticsMS: Calculate "Generated Energy by Prosumer"
AnalyticsMS -> AnalyticsMS: Calculate "Consumed Energy by Prosumer"
AnalyticsMS -> AnalyticsMS: Calculate "Average SoC"

== Dashboard Event Publishing ==

AnalyticsMS -> KafkaZone: Publish Event (Key: ZoneID)
AnalyticsMS -> KafkaGenPros: Publish Event (Key: ProsumerID)
AnalyticsMS -> KafkaConsPros: Publish Event (Key: ProsumerID)
AnalyticsMS -> KafkaSoC: Publish Event (Key: ZoneID)

KafkaZone --> AnalyticsMS: Ack
KafkaGenPros --> AnalyticsMS: Ack
KafkaConsPros --> AnalyticsMS: Ack
KafkaSoC --> AnalyticsMS: Ack

AnalyticsMS --> Kong: 200 OK (Analytics Complete)
Kong --> Camunda: Process Completed \nSuccessfully
@enduml